{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">2104L</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$0.07 – $0.76 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">250</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">7 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">250</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.76 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.44 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">1000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.32 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">2500</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.18 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">5000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.11 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">10000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.09 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">25000</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$0.07 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Laminated Wallet Cards give you high impact advertising with two-sided imprint, a variety of stock art options, and a high-quality laminated finish.</li><li>Choice of stock art backgrounds or create your own.</li><li>Price includes printing in full-color (four color process) on one or both sides.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Choose Imprint for Your Product</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Choose &lt;i&gt;either&lt;/i&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Full-Color&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;Pantone Color Match&lt;/strong&gt; (additional charge will incur).</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/9/A937C34BEB3ECA7AAABFC78D50F81044.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">4CP</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">4 Color Process</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Exact color matches, metallic or fluorescent colors &lt;strong&gt;are not available&lt;/strong&gt;.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/6/F6272A4927BE0036563348FA77497804.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9001</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pantone Color Match</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Printed to match Coated Pantone Color Bridge book.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$50.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Copy Change</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Up to 10 copy changes available at standard pricing. Please contact us for a quote on 11 or more copy changes.\r\n\r\nSelect the number of additional changes and use the Choices text box to type in instructions. If you have different copy for the same product, you may group the copy changes on the same order. \r\n\r\n&lt;strong&gt;NOTE:&lt;/strong&gt; There is only 1 copy change charge no matter how many colors change if printing is in full color (four color process). &lt;font color=&quot;b31b34&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Published minimum quantities for all products apply for copy changes. Copy Changes are limited to changing 6 lines of copy, a photo and a logo. In addition, the items must all have a common background or main layout that does not change.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;i&gt;Please Note: Once an order is submitted to factory, copy changes cannot be added.&lt;/i&gt;\r\n&lt;hr&gt;</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">9006</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Click to Choose Stock Wallet Card Art</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Click on Thumbnail to see larger image.\r\n\r\nPlease specify letter identification of layout, or calendar year (if applicable).</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/6/0/6098E45AADC6CC3AD820B0F6E8A08711.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">A</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Year-at-a-Glance Calendar</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Calendar Style A&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify calendar year and color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/6/5/65470B08C7A6A8F28F3A1EC0C2CBAD0C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">AB</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Year-at-a-Glance Calendar</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Calendar Style AB&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify calendar year and color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/8/A87AD93D34E771F62366861DDF1A549D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Percent Interest Chart</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Percent Interest Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/5/E5CC80925C9CBECC71C8E1CB21D10CD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">BC</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Conversion Chart</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Conversion Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/C/1/C1717BC5BA511B7843FC70AFB89AD9E2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">BJ</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blackjack Tip Chart</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Blackjack Tip Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/B/9B2D468355F5180631A6A89F63C2421A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">C</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Balanced Diet</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Balanced Diet Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/D/E/DEF8EC7A0526A4802FFBFD7E0FCF1B12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border bo