entral.com/uploads/8/E/8E90E46A728698E9ED9EEE499E2726EF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">HI</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Business Principles</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Business Principles Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nArt comes standard in full-color printing.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/7/F74E5E5A435E12D295AB223A1DEB4106.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">I</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Religious Holidays</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Religious Holidays Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nArt comes standard in full-color printing.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/3/B/3B9189708119089FB7B994E0B8813237.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">IJ</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Fractions/Decimals</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Fractions and Decimals Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/7/F79A8EA983C3DFAD1498760F37670335.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">J</p><p class=\"text-[12px]