t used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/5/455005C539E13B45A375A1EAD85D200E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PH</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Poker Chart</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Poker Hand Chart&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/0/1/01C3223B9474E27ADCC5626D41D272BF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PN</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Phone Number Buttons and Alphabet</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Phone Number Buttons and Alphabet&lt;/strong&gt;\nArt comes standard in colors shown.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/6/B662F152288E93085981C0A5B72C226E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">R-2%</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Monthly Payments</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Amortization Chart Potrait&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/F/4FF7BFD4E7A4A7F168A82A4AFC83A8B0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">R-4%</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Monthly Payments</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Amortization Chart Potrait&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/2/B/2BD06200E1B6BBE7DB56A76FF4B0D4A9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">S</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">6 Month Double Sided Calendar</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Calendar Style S&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify calendar year and color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/D/B/DB2005845CD21A901AD6B99B336912A7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">T</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Equal Payments</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">&lt;strong&gt;Amortization Chart Landscape&lt;/strong&gt;\nSpecify color(s) you want used on your purchase order.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Proof Options</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9ONLINE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Internet Color Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Online Proofing is to show you color and/or color breaks, but IS NOT an exact color matching proofing system. Output from laser printers, ink-jet printers or what you view on your computer monitor cannot be matched. These methods are subjective and may not accurately represent your final printed product.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9DIGITAL</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Digital Press Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Color press proofs are a close representation of the color of your product.  Press proofs are available on four-color process items.  Please note that wall calendar/booklet digital press proof sheets are printed on a digital press. The final product may be printed on a conventional press, therefore, a 5% difference in color, contrast and saturation may occur.   This proof will not be trimmed, stapled, UV-coated, or feature a heavy cover.  &lt;strong&gt;Press proofs are sent via overnight shipping at customer's expense.  If you do not want your proofs expedited, please contact Customer Service. Note pads not available for this service.&lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$30.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9002</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Production Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Actual printed &amp; laminated product proofs. Pre-Production Proofs for Wall Calendar/Booklet Pre-Production Proof are printed on a digital press. The final product may be printed on a conventional press, therefore, a 5% difference in color, contrast and saturation may occur.&lt;strong&gt;Product proofs are sent via overnight shipping at customer's expense.  If you do not want your proofs expedited, please contact Customer Service.  Printed product proofs &amp; shipping are FREE OF CHARGE on orders of $6,250(G) or more.   Pantone® color matches are billed at $50(C) per color on all product proofs.&lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$80.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Laminated Wallet Card - 3.5x2.25 (2-Sided) - 14 pt.. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">2104L</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>7 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">250</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}